# Whether login shells run the whimsical extras (fortune, cowsay, BOFH
# excuses, calendar, weather) after fastfetch. run.sh prompts for this
# interactively the first time it runs and writes the answer here — you
# don't need to set it by hand, but you can to skip the prompt or change
# your mind later (then re-run ./run.sh).
WHIMSY_ENABLED=false
